<HEADLINE> Tehran Stock Exchange Index up 3.65 Points </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
TEHRAN, August 22 (Xinhua) -- The general price index at
Tehran Stock Exchange stood at 1,476.59 points on Saturday, up
3.65 points compared to the figure on Wednesday.
</P>
<P>
A total of 655,507 shares worth over 2.07 billion rials
(376,000 U.S. dollars) changed hands in 583 turns for 378
applicants. The shares of 33 companies made gains while those of
eight others declined. 
