<TEXT>
<P>
WASHINGTON, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Concrete barriers were
erected around the Washington monument and tourists's bags
searched on Saturday, showing the United States has been
heightening security following U.S. missile attacks against
alleged terrorist sites in Sudan and Afghanistan.
</P>
