<HEADLINE> Nigeria,Chad,Niger to Combat Crimes at Lake Chad </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, August 22 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria, Chad and Niger have
decided to set up a joint committee to combat increasing
incidents of banditry in Lake Chad area, where they share a
common border
</P>
<P>
The decision was made at a joint meeting attended by Nigerian
