<HEADLINE> Hong Kong Climbers Missing on Mt. Bogda </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
URUMQI, western China, August 23 (Xinhua) -- Three Hong Kong
climbers remained missing on Sunday on Mt. Bogda in China's
Xinjiang Autonomous Region after attempts in the past week to
locate them all failed.
</P>
<P>
