<P>
TOKYO, August 23 (Xinhua) -- Defending champion Joichiro
Tatsuyoshi of Japan defeated American challenger Paul Ayala to
retain the World Boxing Council (WBC) bantamweight title on
Sunday in Yokohama, Japan.
</P>
