up arms against the U.S. in retaliation against the U.S. bombings.
</P>
<P>
Alkozli claimed there were no terrorist training camps in
Afghanistan, and said the Afghan community was opposed to
terrorism.
</P>
<P>
Carrying anti-US banners, the protesters met at Sydney Town
Hall before marching to the U.S. consulate in Martin Place.
